{"tid":885722,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"落實 FB 搵錢大計   WhatsApp 廣告短期內殺到","createTime":"2018-11-01T14:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T03:42:51.000Z","uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e565a3a1d32d4d477bcb3f60bcf7c77d3be006e","tid":885722,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\">落實 FB 搵錢大計   WhatsApp 廣告短期內殺到</div><br />\n<br />\n今年 9 月 WhatsApp 創辦人 Brian Acton 透露，Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg 就在收購完成前，已經有如何藉著 WhatsApp 搵錢的全盤計劃。如今 WhatsApp 的副總裁 Chris Daniels 確認其中一個搵錢大計，在 App 內刊登廣告會在短期內殺到。<br />\n<br />\n落實 FB 搵錢大計   WhatsApp 廣告短期內殺到<br />\n<br />\n現時活躍使用人數超過 4.5 億的 WhatsApp，用戶很快就會在 Status 狀態功能內見到 WhatsApp 推送的廣告內容，Daniels 表示這是 Facebook 訂下的主要賺錢模式，讓企業可以透過 WhatsApp 接觸人群。Facebook 強調用戶的數據會點對點加密，所以將不會透過 WhatsApp 收集任何數據。<br />\n<br />\n廣告內容會由 Facebook 自家的廣告系統提供，估計會以用戶在 Facebook 登記的電話號碼去跟 WhatsApp 帳號掛鈎，利用用戶於 Facebook 上的活動向 WhatsApp 推送對應的廣告內容。暫時 WhatsApp 未公佈何時會正式推送廣告，但早前有傳 iOS 用戶會率先見到。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：phonearena<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4429/211795/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4429%2F211795%2F1%2F&d=rhwCuyOkgID7OebO1yMOFozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e0f3308a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4429/211795/1/</a>"},{"pid":"86f30b5ed0bccbfb503346b80f249acbc53e1ba0","tid":885722,"uid":131933,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"傻仔先用wtsapp<br />\ntg各方面領先<br />\n<br />\n而家wtsapp功能全部都係跟住tg行<br />\n最on9係一定要比電話number人先搵到<br />\n唔係佢出先食左條水邊會有人用<br />\n好似八達通一樣咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83db2a53e5160d8c8e209dbaca02843e4fed6c22","tid":885722,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"a5ccc6be69ca56485dee054e0e97e6b562a01be6","tid":885722,"uid":105553,"like":2,"dislike":